## Methodology

Our three-phase approach:

```text
Phase 1: Repository Discovery
├── GitHub API searches
├── Repository-level patterns
└── Code-level patterns
          ↓
Phase 2: Indicator-Based Pre-Selection
├── 10 LiaScript indicators
├── Strong vs. weak classification
└── 75,260 candidates identified
          ↓
Phase 3: AI-Based Validation
├── llama3.3:70b model
├── Binary classification
└── {{ stats.total_courses }} validated courses
```

